{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_ios_pwa_design_ios_pwa", "label": "Polimento iOS do PWA", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-ios-pwa-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Instalado via 'Adicionar \u00e0 Tela de In\u00edcio', o app deve ficar indistingu\u00edvel de nativo \u2014 sem App Store (US$ 99/ano s\u00f3 se o PWA n\u00e3o convencer). Problema: iOS n\u00e3o aceita SVG como apple-touch-icon (\u00edcone sa\u00eda em branco) e sem metas iOS abria com barra do Safari."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_ios_pwa_design_icones_png_ios", "label": "\u00cdcones PNG iOS/maskable (apple-touch-icon, 192/512)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-ios-pwa-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Gerados do icon.svg atual (desenho intocado), vers\u00e3o full-bleed sem cantos arredondados \u2014 iOS/maskable arredondam sozinhos. Gera\u00e7\u00e3o via script descart\u00e1vel com puppeteer-core + Edge headless \u2014 nada de depend\u00eancia nova no repo; PNGs commitados."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_ios_pwa_design_splash_escura", "label": "Splash escura por resolu\u00e7\u00e3o de iPhone", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-ios-pwa-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "PNGs #070c18 com \u00edcone centrado, um por resolu\u00e7\u00e3o comum de iPhone, via apple-touch-startup-image + media queries \u2014 elimina o flash de tela branca na abertura."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_ios_pwa_design_ios_pwa", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_ios_pwa_design_icones_png_ios", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED